                                        <div class="carousel-caption d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                                            <small class="small-title">A Community That Gives Back</small>

                                            <h1>Connect, <span class="text-warning">Share,</span> Care </h1>

                                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
